      "name": "Mesh convergence study — FDA generic centrifugal pump",
      "description": "Grid refinement study across three mesh densities (coarse 2.1 M cells, medium 5.8 M cells, fine 14.2 M cells). Richardson extrapolation applied to scalar hemolysis index. GCI reported at 3.4% for fine-to-medium transition. Acceptable for MRL 5 discretization requirements.",
      "evidenceTimestamp": "2024-01-20T14:30:00Z"
