    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. Experimental comparison yielded MAPE of 9.8%, within the pre-specified 15% threshold. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed for primary input parameters. The package is accepted pending resolution of model-form uncertainty and use-error gaps in a subsequent assessment cycle.",
